ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Are your weapons compatible with both organic and cybernetic components?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Absolutely! Our weaponry is specially designed to be wielded by cyborg ninjas, featuring adaptive grips and neural interfaces. Whether you're mostly flesh or mostly machine, our gear will feel like a natural extension of your body.

FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What types of cybernetic enhancements do you offer?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: We offer a wide range of cutting-edge cybernetic enhancements, including optical upgrades, neural processors, stealth cloaking systems, and high-performance limb replacements tailored for ninja agility and strength.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Are your weapons compatible with standard ninja gear?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Absolutely! Our cyborg-optimized weapons are designed to seamlessly integrate with traditional ninja equipment. From plasma-edged katanas to silent, neural-linked shurikens, we ensure maximum compatibility and stealth.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Do you offer maintenance services for cyborg components?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, we provide comprehensive maintenance and upgrade services for all our cyborg components. Our team of expert technicians can perform everything from routine diagnostics to complete system overhauls, ensuring your cybernetic enhancements are always mission-ready.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: What payment methods do you accept?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: We accept a variety of payment methods, including cryptocurrency, untraceable digital credits, and rare earth minerals. For security reasons, we do not accept traditional banking methods.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Is there a warranty on your products?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: All our cyborg enhancements and ninja gear come with a standard 1-year warranty against manufacturing defects. We also offer an extended 'Shadow Warrior' warranty that covers damage sustained during covert operations, available for an additional fee.
